N Queens-

a) Search Space-
    Brute force: 8^8
    One per row: 8!
    Backtracking: much less due to pruning

b) Optimized Pseudocode-
    b[row] = col
    ok(r, c):
    for i from 0 to r-1:
        if b[i] == c or abs(i-r) == abs(b[i]-c):
            return false
    return true

c) Trace for N = 4 (short)-
    Row 0 -> Col 1
    Row 1 -> Col 3
    Row 2 -> Col 0
    Row 3 -> Col 2
    Solution found

d) Find Only One Solution-
    Return true when solution found
    Stop further calls

e) Forbidden Squares-
    Before placing queen:
    if cell is forbidden: skip
    Time reduces as choices reduce
